### Create new account
POST {{host}}/auth/users/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "email": "{{email}}",
    "password": "{{password}}",
    "re_password": "{{password}}"
}


### Login
POST {{host}}/auth/token/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}


### Logout
POST {{host}}/auth/token/logout/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

